{"type":"message","id":"14bfec90","parentId":"e9f52bc6","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:35:00.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 太好了，说明核心签名链路已经定位到了。  \n\n现在基本可以认为关键算法是这条：\n\n- 先拼基础参数：\n  - `authtimeout=518400`\n  - `format=json`\n  - `hlsflag=0`\n  - `httpsflag=1`\n  - `userid=...`\n  - `videoid=...`\n- 再追加：\n  - `time=<毫秒时间戳>`\n  - `salt=<固定盐值>`\n- 最后做：\n  - `MD5(...)`\n  - 转大写\n- 把结果作为 `hash` 传给：\n  - `https://p.bokecc.com/api/mobile?...&time=...&hash=...`\n\n也就是大致：\n\n```text\nhash = MD5(\n  \"authtimeout=518400&format=json&hlsflag=0&httpsflag=1&userid=USER_ID&videoid=VIDEO_ID&time=TS_MS&salt=SALT\"\n).upper()\n```\n\n接下来你可以做 3 件事里的任意一个：\n\n1. **验证算法**\n   我可以帮你用一个 `videoid` 实际请求，确认能不能稳定拿到 `playurl`。\n\n2. **提炼成最小 PoC**\n   我可以把它整理成最短版本，方便你后面复用/写到别的语言里。\n\n3. **继续逆向上游**\n   我可以帮你判断：\n   - `salt` 是硬编码出来的，还是接口配置下发的\n   - `USER_ID` 是否固定租户 ID\n   - 有没有额外风控参数没被你当前样本覆盖到\n\n如果你要，我下一条可以直接给你一份**超简洁的算法说明 + JS/Python 双版本实现**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c723e1e735810690169d71e5d3c4c819480145ca3a6c8feaa\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":25180,"output":401,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25581,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775705691402,"responseId":"resp_0c723e1e735810690169d71e5c5bc08194851918e469632452"}}
